# AI Service API Keys (Optional)
# Add these to enable external AI features in your chatbot

# OpenAI API Key (Most capable AI responses)
# Get from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-key-here

# Groq API Key (Free and fast AI alternative)
# Get from: https://console.groq.com/keys
# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_your-groq-key-here

# RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) Configuration
# Pinecone Vector Database for document storage and retrieval
# Get from: https://app.pinecone.io
# PINECONE_API_KEY=your-pinecone-api-key-here

# Note: 
# - Uncomment the lines above and add your actual API keys
# - The chatbot works perfectly without these keys (uses pattern matching)
# - Keys are optional for enhanced AI responses
# - RAG requires both OPENAI_API_KEY and PINECONE_API_KEY
# - For Vercel deployment, add these as environment variables in the dashboard
